> <OLD>
>
> There was a quirk of the opticbrow from DINOBOT, "Oh, I was not aware your
> presence was..  Shall we say so high up the command hierarchy, TARANTALUS.
> Have things been reordered over in my abscence, or is this somewhat of an
> impromptu self-promotion?"  Then again, he and VICE GRIP were both total
> neophytes to the new PREDACON unit, CRYOTEK, HYDRAS, CYCLONUS, and SCOURGE
> were all missing, along with SKORPONOK...
>
> But, as summoned, DINOBOT went up and over towards the bridge as he was
> commanded.

<NEW>

Yes, there were many missing - JHIAXUS and SCORPONOK were both missing
and have been for some time, but HYDRAS, CYCLONUS and SCOURGE were
also missing more recently and even CRYOTEK!

It was as if the PREDACONS couldn't keep a leader a round without it
being lost or stolen!

SKYSHADOW gave DINOBOT a 'look' as he was just in the dark about
TARANTULUS' sudden self promotion.

As they came to the command center the large form of BRUTICUS-X was
standing at the door way in his dreaded CERBERUS beast mode, his three
heads each looking around than at the group. He quietly stood as the
door opened and allowed entrance to the bridge.

http://tfwiki.net/w2/images2/3/39/RID_Bruticus_Toy.jpg

The bridge itself looked well apponted. It had a singular command
chair with Navigation and Helm control towards the front of the bridge
and other stations lining it along the walls.

"Greetings." TARANTULUS said as IGUANUS and SCAREM stepped aside so
that SKYSHADOW and DINOBOT could get a clear view of the new PREDACON
'commander' "I see you have met my staff." There was a wicked chuckle.

"Since when does the help sit in the command chair?" SKYSHADOW said
menacingly as he stepped foward.

The high pitched sounds of weapons being charged up could suddenly be
heard as IGUANUS and SCAREM took aim on SKYSHADOW and DINOBOT.

"You will mind your words Skyshadow." TARANTULUS said as he leaned
back in the chair, confident and smug. "Or I will show you the error
of your ways." He chuckled as he rubbed his hands together
mischieviously, yes he evidently had plans.

"It was me you came to meet." said a powerful contralto voice as a
female in dark armor stepped out of a door that had just swished open.

http://tfwiki.net/w2/images2/a/a2/BW_Antagony_boxart.jpg

(TAG)

- Preston
